    The Doubling Cube is always in effect in Tournmenets and when
    played in Backgammon Clubs. But when the game is played in private,
    the two players agree before starting the game, If Doubling Cube
    will be in effect or not. So in your case I would suggest that
    the two players can agree through the chat mode and either one
    presses a button to choose the mode (With or without Cube)

    Now that this is settled, here are some rules that apply when
    the game is being played with the Doubling Cube:

 1. Doubling should be in effect only after each player has rolled
    twice the dice.

 2. Either player can double when the Cube is in the center of the
    board.

 3. If a player wishes to Double he can do so ONLY before he rolls the dice.

 4. When a player doubles, he has to wait for his opponent's decision.
    And it is only after the ACCEPTANCE by his opponent that he has
    the right to roll and make his move. Of course if opponent refuses
    the Double, then the game is over and a new game starts.

 5. Once the Doubling Cube has been moved from its initial position
    (center of the board) then the right to Double goes ONLY to the
    player who owns the CUBE.


(F)orfeit
----------

    This option is created to avoid to play long games that the outcome
    is 99% predictable.
    The following is the way this option should work:-

    The losing side might decide to forfeit the game and lose a point,
    but the winning side might not accept this arrangement, thinking
    that he can gammon his opponent and win 2 points. After some
    bargaining between the players they might not agree to stop the
    game, so the game continues. What I would suggest is that the
    players can do all the bargaining through the Chat mode and once
    they agree to stop the game either player should be able to press a
    key for a simple forfeit (1 x Cube Value, if Cube in effect) and
    a gammon forfet ( 2 x Cube value, if cube in effect). The whole idea
    of Forfeit is to save wasted time..! But the winning side should not
    be penalized by giving him only 1 point if he thinks he can gammon.

